origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "CyberSecurityInsurance.get_coverage_and_cost",
        "description": "获取特定网络安全保险产品的覆盖范围和费用信息。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "product_name",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "保险产品的名称。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "coverage_and_cost",
                "description": "包含覆盖范围和费用的详细信息。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "CyberSecurityInsurance.get_network_info",
        "description": "获取当前网络的基本信息，用于网络安全保险的评估。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "network_info",
                "description": "网络的基本信息，如IP地址、子网掩码等。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "CyberSecurityInsurance.recommend_products",
        "description": "根据提供的网络信息推荐适合的网络安全保险产品。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "network_info",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "网络的基本信息。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "insurance_products",
                "description": "推荐的网络安全保险产品列表。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "CyberSecurityInsurance.provide_selection_advice",
        "description": "根据覆盖范围、费用和网络信息提供保险产品选择的建议。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "coverage_and_cost",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "保险产品的覆盖范围和费用信息。"
            },
            {
                "name": "network_info",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "网络的基本信息。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "selection_advice",
                "description": "关于选择哪个保险产品的建议。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "CyberSecurityInsurance.compare_products",
        "description": "比较多个网络安全保险产品的覆盖范围和费用，提供详细的对比报告。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "product_list",
                "type": "LIST",
                "description": "需要比较的保险产品列表。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "comparison_report",
                "description": "包含各产品覆盖范围和费用对比的详细报告。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "CyberSecurityInsurance.check_vulnerabilities",
        "description": "检查当前网络中存在的潜在安全漏洞，并提供修复建议。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "network_info",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "网络的基本信息。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "vulnerability_report",
                "description": "包含发现的漏洞和修复建议的报告。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "CyberSecurityInsurance.estimate_risk_level",
        "description": "根据网络信息和已知漏洞，估算当前网络的风险等级。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "network_info",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "网络的基本信息。"
            },
            {
                "name": "vulnerability_report",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "包含发现的漏洞和修复建议的报告。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "risk_level",
                "description": "估算的网络风险等级。"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
